Usage: configure [opts]
General Options:
	-c | -cc cc
		default: cc

	-h | --help
		print this help

Installation Options
	-p | --prefix path
		default: /usr/local

	-b | --bindir path
		default: $PREFIX/bin

	-d | --datadir path
		default: $PREFIX/share

	-D | --docdir path
		default: $PREFIX/share/doc

	-m | --mandir path
		default: $PREFIX/share/man
